Regarding future work, we first plan to perform more case studies to empirically  validate the different quality aspects in more detail, specifically their relevance for prac- titioners and how to deal with them in different process stages. Second, we want to  apply this method to other ML problems (like regression, or unsupervised problems)  and learn about the impact on the quality model. Third, we intend to package our in- sights into development guidelines for quality-aware ML systems.
